{"tid":2292872,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港人防災記　炒Tesla 搵快錢　開虛擬銀行戶口走資　90後港女：真的很憂慮","createTime":"2020-11-19T23:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T00:03:46.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44616894543f89b6be27dde3a9d3cc2a8f9f709f","tid":2292872,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T23:56:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U7bK3KcA25Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU7bK3KcA25Y&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=1d322044\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U7bK3KcA25Y</a><br />\n...<br />\n她開立的證券戶口，雖然有存款保障，但始終不是銀行，狡兔三窟，她需要更多的安全感，於是她又開立了一個外國虛擬銀行戶口，到六月，國安法壓境，之後不斷有美國制裁香港銀行的消息傳出，她更加害怕，「始終人未走，每個月還是要留大約一萬元的生活開支，還有一些備用資金，放在現在的銀行裡真的很不安全。」於是，她又跟機開設香港的美資銀行戶口，打工仔不便請假跑分行，於是在網上開戶，等了兩星期，音訊全無，還是要到分行了解，去到銀行，見到門口已打了兩條蛇餅，眼淚幾乎奪眶而出。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_759390_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_759390_0&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=77024afa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_759390_0&h=678759ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_759390_0</a>"},{"pid":"67c617f6579518a0518680e4282bb51312ecd489","tid":2292872,"uid":72173,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:02:30.000Z","msg":"升左叫投資，輸左叫賭錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e20aa6155f2ec14ace08009c723f59521e6bc7d","tid":2292872,"uid":311626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:03:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾報，又篤灰"}]}